title: Investing in Tech Stocks: The Big 5
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Alex Eule discuss the outlook for Apple, Alphabet, Amazon.com, Facebook, and Microsoft. Plus, GameStop's strange earnings call.
